[The government update has resumed for North Kivu and now also includes Equateur.

Note: 2 new confirmed cases in a new location: Bolomba, Equateur province. Good news that there are no new confirmed cases in North Kivu or Ituri for 44 days.

Helen Branswell tweets (https://twitter.com/HelenBranswell): "The case count in Equateur Province in western DRC is up to 16 (13 confirmed, 3 probables) & 10 people have died...." These numbers are higher than the report above likely because they apparently are 1 day later than the report posted. - Mod.LK]

